data.description: Beautifully updated home in convenient location.  Easy access to Southside, downtown, Hitchcock Woods and much more.  Home has like new carpet and ceramic tile floors, newer LTV Luxury flooring.  Level lot in front with beautiful wooded view in back.  Very Private.  Kitchen has updated solid surface counters and Newer Stainless steel appliances.   Spacious Greatroom with vaulted ceiling and  fireplace and Plantation Shutters.  PRIMARY BEDROOM ON MAIN LEVEL with walk-in-closet and ensuite bath.  There are 2 spaciious bedrooms with jack and jill bath on 2nd floor.  PLUS a large bonus room.   See this one today!
